text: Randall Adam Fine (born April 20, 1974) is an American politician and former gambling industry businessman. He has been the U.S. representative for Florida's 6th congressional district since April 2025. He is a member of the Republican Party. Before, he was in the Florida Senate from 2024 to 2025.
